7873:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7874:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7875:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
